      <title>土耳其免除银行通胀会计核算​​以促进盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/turkey-spares-banks-from-inflation-accounting-in-earnings-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其银行业监管机构表示，银行和金融公司在 2025 年将不必实施通胀会计，这将在公布全年业绩之前消除银行盈利面临的巨大负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/turkey-spares-banks-from-inflation-accounting-in-earnings-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:46:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
